    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1892-01-13T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1892-01-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="276" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d276">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Egan</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Blaine</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of
                                    the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Valparaiso</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1892-01-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 13, 1892</hi>.</date>
                            (Received 3 p.m.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Have just placed in safety on board <hi rend="italic">Yorktown</hi> remaining
                        five refugees from my legation, also two refugees from Spanish legation, who
                        were accompanied by Spanish minister. Italian minister also accompanied.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Egan</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
